Welcome to the IMACC Corporation Home Page

We are located in Dalton Georgia and serve a wide customer base.  Our Nationwide Collection program and Transportation Services are at your service for empty packaging collection and recycling.  Our products include reconditioned Intermediate Bulk Containers (IBC's), Poly Drums and new Packagings.  Please tour our site using the navigation links and learn about our facility capabilities, recycling services and products.




IMACC opens Louisville Kentucky Facility!


	 
	
 


IMACC - Dalton Production




We are located near our wide customer base in Dalton Georgia. We also serve remote customers by Nationwide Collection.

	 
	
	 
	
 


Raw Material Storage




High Storage Capacity and wide selection of Packaging Types

	 


	 
	
 


Plastic Recycling






Efficient plastic recovery and recycling.

	 
	
	 
	
 


Reconditioned Intermediate Bulk Containers




This packaging style is a Round Tubular Cage on a Steel Pallet.
